  "detailed_description": "Resurrected from extinction on a remote island chain, dinosaurs have escaped to wreak chaos! An elite mercenary team is now sent to eliminate the primal threat...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ROAR POWER!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321360/extras/ed8b9efa663747b830009f534f3c6cc0.poster.avif?t=1745496059\" width=540 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321360/extras/ed8b9efa663747b830009f534f3c6cc0.webm?t=1745496059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321360/extras/ed8b9efa663747b830009f534f3c6cc0.mp4?t=1745496059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take control of <strong>12 deadly dinosaur classes</strong>, from sneaky Spitters to towering Tyrants, all of them ruthless and <i>very </i>hungry. Each species has unique traits and attacks, so unleash your <i>Roar Ability </i>to gain a tactical advantage!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NOT JUST A WALK IN THE PARK.</strong> </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321360/extras/ba9c39f09b8bc1ada68144af9de5a469.poster.avif?t=1745496059\" width=540 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321360/extras/ba9c39f09b8bc1ada68144af9de5a469.webm?t=1745496059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321360/extras/ba9c39f09b8bc1ada68144af9de5a469.mp4?t=1745496059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The mercenary team uses an arsenal of devastating weaponry and gadgets to send these bloodthirsty beasts back to the Cretaceous. Select from five distinct human classes, each with their own special utilities. Watch your back, or <strong>you're extinct!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR MISSION</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321360/extras/67dd1642becf194db358efb8740ecf6a.poster.avif?t=1745496059\" width=540 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321360/extras/67dd1642becf194db358efb8740ecf6a.webm?t=1745496059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321360/extras/67dd1642becf194db358efb8740ecf6a.mp4?t=1745496059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fight to the top of the food chain in all out prehistoric warfare!<br></li><li>Work together to reach rescue, or ensure the humans never leave the island!<br></li><li>Go challenge yourself to a never-ending onslaught of AI dinosaurs in co-op.<br></li><li>Stalk the humans as an invisible raptor, or band together to take it down.<br></li><li>Steal eggs from dinosaur nests or protect your unhatched babies!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>65 MILLION YEARS OF FASHION</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321360/extras/958022e505be491e21aa65bf7176f338.poster.avif?t=1745496059\" width=540 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321360/extras/958022e505be491e21aa65bf7176f338.webm?t=1745496059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321360/extras/958022e505be491e21aa65bf7176f338.mp4?t=1745496059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Deck out your dinos with model mutations, bling out your guns, or drive your enemies mad with taunts! Unlock skins and more as free drops, buy or sell on ]Steam Marketplace, and earn <i>Extinction Points</i> (EXP) to rank up and unlock cosmetics.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BIGGER. BETTER. MORE TEETH.</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321360/extras/943894f133ecb9269503b8c4fda775c1.poster.avif?t=1745496059\" width=540 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321360/extras/943894f133ecb9269503b8c4fda775c1.webm?t=1745496059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321360/extras/943894f133ecb9269503b8c4fda775c1.mp4?t=1745496059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Featuring <strong>NEW </strong>species, gametypes, weapons, maps, and MORE, <i>Primal Carnage: Extinction</i> takes dinosaur combat to the next level! And we're not done yet...",
